text: Priyanka Karki (born 27 February 1987 in kathmandu, Nepal) is a Nepali actress, model, dancer , VJ and singer. She is one of the top actresses from Nepal. She is also Former Miss Teen Nepal. She has won many National Film Awards. She is a versatile Nepali actress well known by her superhit movies: Chakka Panja, Cha ekan Cha, Nai Nabhannu La etc. == References == == Other websites == * Category:Nepalese movie actors Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Kathmandu Category:Nepalese models Category:Nepalese singers Category:Nepalese beauty pageant winners Category:Nepalese Hindus
